Record Class Bill

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
Model.Bill
Record Components:
id - unique identifier of the bill
clientName - name of the client who made the order
productName - name of the ordered product
quantity - quantity of the product ordered
totalPrice - total price for the ordered quantity
createdAt - timestamp when the bill was created
public record Bill(int id, String clientName, String productName, int quantity, double totalPrice, LocalDateTime createdAt) extends Record
Immutable Bill record representing an entry in the Log table. Contains information about the order such as client, product, quantity, total price, and timestamp when the bill was created.
